OL,3,CPopular diving platform to reopen
OL,4,Cafter community protests
OL,6,FA popular free outdoor diving platform
OL,7,Fin Guernsey will reopen to the public
OL,8,Fthis weekend following months of
OL,9,Fpublic pressure.
OL,11,FThe board, installed in the 1920s at
OL,12,FLa Vallette Bathing Pools, was closed
OL,13,Fand due to be removed in February
OL,14,Fafter it failed a health and safety
OL,15,Fassessment.
OL,17,FHundreds of local people came out to
OL,18,Fprotest the decision and stood around
OL,19,FLadies' Pool, leading the Government
OL,20,Fto pause its removal.
