OL,3,CPopular diving platform to reopen
OL,4,Cafter community protests
OL,6,FOfficials said the necessary changes
OL,7,Fto increase the water depth and stop
OL,8,Fleaks would cost #1 million and even
OL,9,Fthen, the area would need to be
OL,10,Fsupervised at all times.
OL,12,FSince then, politicians have worked
OL,13,Fwith the community, businesses and the
OL,14,FHealth and Safety Executive (HSE) to
OL,15,Ffind a solution.
