OL,3,CPopular diving platform to reopen
OL,4,Cafter community protests
OL,6,FA large amount of silt, rubble and
OL,7,Fbedrock has been cleared to increase
OL,8,Fthe pool's depth to 3.5 metres around
OL,9,Fthe platform - above the minimum 3.2-
OL,10,Fmetre clearance required by World
OL,11,FAquatics and British Standards.
OL,13,FAdrian Sarchet is part of the working
OL,14,Fgroup to reopen the platform and adds:
OL,15,F"We should all feel blessed to live in
OL,16,Fa place where magic like this can
OL,17,Fhappen.
