OL,3,CPopular diving platform to reopen
OL,4,Cafter community protests
OL,6,F"The community spoke, government
OL,7,Flistened, and local business
OL,8,Ffacilitated a solution largely for
OL,9,Ffree.
OL,11,F"The cast of faces that has made this
OL,12,Fhappen is too large to thank
OL,13,Findividually here, but each and every
OL,14,Fone of you has my thanks."
OL,16,FThe States says further safety
OL,17,Fimprovements will be made over the
OL,18,Fsummer, including better steps and non-
OL,19,Fslip surfaces, leading to sign-off
OL,20,Ffrom the HSE to reopen it straight
OL,21,Faway for public use.
